# accessLog

**Instance Property**

A snapshot of the network playback log for the movie player if it is playing a network stream.

## Declaration

```swift
var accessLog: MPMovieAccessLog! { get }
```

## Discussion

Can be `nil`. For information about movie access logs, refer to [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPMovieAccessLog].

## Retrieving movie logs

- **errorLog**: A snapshot of the playback failure error log for the movie player if it is playing a network stream.
